.TH BTOON 1 "November 2025" "btoon 0.0.1" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
btoon - a command-line tool for converting between JSON and BTOON
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B btoon
[\fIcommand\fR] [\fIinput\fR] [\fIoutput\fR] [\fIoptions\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B btoon
is a command-line tool for converting between the JSON and BTOON binary formats.
.SH COMMANDS
.TP
.B encode
Encode a JSON file to BTOON.
.TP
.B decode
Decode a BTOON file to JSON.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B --compress
Enable compression (default: zlib).
.TP
.B --version
Print version information.
.TP
.B --help
Print usage information.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
.B btoon encode input.json output.btoon
Encode a JSON file to BTOON.
.TP
.B btoon decode input.btoon output.json
Decode a BTOON file to JSON.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR btoon (7)
.SH BUGS
No known bugs.
